feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 02, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pvq1719930730570.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pvq1719930730570.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pvq1719930730570.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lfj1665702577355\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $instancepath\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"lfj1665702577355___instancepath_270184\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the path with which the current component instance is registered.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__topic_d84743e1_d84744e1_d84745e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__p_d84746e1_d84747e1_d84748e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancepath</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code> }</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__topic_d56172e1_d56173e1_d56174e1_d56175e1_d56176e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d342639e75\">\n                       Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__d6052e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__d6052e20__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__d6052e20__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__d6052e20__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lfj1665702577355__d6052e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstanceName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lfj1665702577355__d6052e20__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lfj1665702577355__d6052e20__entry__3\">Name of component instance; optional. If\n\t\t\t\t omitted, the current instance is used. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__topic_d56177e1_d56178e1_d56179e1_d56180e1_d56181e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d342639e129\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__li_d34577e1_d34578e1_d34579e1\">Name of the path for the current instance in uppercase.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__li_d34580e1_d34581e1_d34582e1\">Empty string (\"\"), if the current application did not register with the Uniface Router when it started.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__topic_d56182e1_d56183e1_d56184e1_d56185e1_d56186e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d342639e144\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__topic_d56187e1_d56188e1_d56189e1_d56190e1_d56191e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d342639e154\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__p_d84764e1_d84765e1_d84766e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancepath</span> function can be useful to pass addressing information to another component instance.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__section_mjd_gx5_xbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d342639e166\">Example: Starting a Component and Passing Data to an Operation</h2>\n<p class=\"p exampletitle\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__p_d84767e1_d84768e1_d84769e1\"> </p>\n<p class=\"p\">The detail trigger of a field in the form COMP1 contains the following\n            code. It starts a new instance of the component COMP2, prepares data for the operation\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">TELL_ME_LATER</code>, then hands the data to the operation.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__pre_dkw_gx5_xbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; field DO_IT\ntrigger detail \n; prepare the data for TELL_ME_LATER\n; prepare the my return address\nvariables\n string MYADRESS\nendvariables\nnewinstance/async \"COMP2\", \"INST2\"\nDATA = ...\nMYADDRESS = \"%%$instancepath:%%$instancename\"\nactivate \"INST2\".TELL_ME_LATER (MYADDRESS, DATA)\nend; detail</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The operation <code class=\"ph codeph\">TELL_ME_LATER</code> does what is required, then\n            sends the result back to the calling instance:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__pre_ekw_gx5_xbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; Component COMP2\n; prepare data to be returned\noperation TELL_ME_LATER\nparams\n string RETURN_ADDRESS : IN\n string DATA : IN\nendparams\nvariables\n string DATAOUT\nendvariables\n...\nDATAOUT = ...\npostmessage \"%%RETURN_ADDRESS\", \"RESULT\", \"%%DATAOUT\"\nend\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">The message is received by the receiveMessage trigger of COMP1:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"lfj1665702577355__pre_fkw_gx5_xbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; component COMP1\ntrigger receiveMessage\nselectcase $msgid\n case \"RESULT\"\n askmess \"Result from %%$msginfo(\"INSTANCENAME\") available in message frame.\"\n putmess \"Received the following result from %%$msginfo(\"SRC\") :\"\n putmess \"%%$msginfo(\"DATA\")\"\n case ...\n...\nendselectcse\nend; receiveMessage</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ksm1665702577277.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instancename</a><p>Return the name of the current component instance.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jdo1665702577507.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$msginfo</a><p>Return the requested information about the latest message.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422993\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422993\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$instancepath Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 02, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $instancepath Return the path with which the current component instance is registered. $instancepath { ( InstanceName ) } Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description InstanceName String Name of component instance; optional. If omitted, the current instance is used. Return Values Name of the path for the current instance in uppercase. Empty string (\"\"), if the current application did not register with the Uniface Router when it started. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The $instancepath function can be useful to pass addressing information to another component instance. Example: Starting a Component and Passing Data to an Operation The detail trigger of a field in the form COMP1 contains the following code. It starts a new instance of the component COMP2, prepares data for the operation TELL_ME_LATER , then hands the data to the operation. ; field DO_IT trigger detail ; prepare the data for TELL_ME_LATER ; prepare the my return address variables string MYADRESS endvariables newinstance/async \"COMP2\", \"INST2\" DATA = ... MYADDRESS = \"%%$instancepath:%%$instancename\" activate \"INST2\".TELL_ME_LATER (MYADDRESS, DATA) end; detail Copy The operation TELL_ME_LATER does what is required, then sends the result back to the calling instance: ; Component COMP2 ; prepare data to be returned operation TELL_ME_LATER params string RETURN_ADDRESS : IN string DATA : IN endparams variables string DATAOUT endvariables ... DATAOUT = ... postmessage \"%%RETURN_ADDRESS\", \"RESULT\", \"%%DATAOUT\" end Copy The message is received by the receiveMessage trigger of COMP1: ; component COMP1 trigger receiveMessage selectcase $msgid case \"RESULT\" askmess \"Result from %%$msginfo(\"INSTANCENAME\") available in message frame.\" putmess \"Received the following result from %%$msginfo(\"SRC\") :\" putmess \"%%$msginfo(\"DATA\")\" case ... ... endselectcse end; receiveMessage Copy Related Links $instancename Return the name of the current component instance. $msginfo Return the requested information about the latest message. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}